Latest Changes:

- added preview of boots to the Edit player window 
- automatic corection of boots when its index is bigger than count of defined boots in the cfg file
( fix for PES 2011 import )
- added kit relink and detailed settings
- improved FM conversion of goalkeepers and fixed weak foot issue
- added automatic detection of player position on the pitch from the FM Print screen
- added support for custom stadium name by team
- updated configuration files commentary.cfg, fake_teams.cfg, boots.cfg, kits.cfg
- improved function to remove fake players
( fake players were moved out of the national teams and replaced by his duplicate in club(s) )
- fixed issue while importing player positions from PES 2011 CSV ( both side issue )
- small improvements in GUI
